If `x, y ∈ v.adicCompletionIntegers ℚ`, then `x = Int.cast z_x` and `y = Int.cast z_y` for some `z_x, z_y ∈ ℤ`. The map `↑(padicEquiv v)` is just `padicEquiv v` applied to the coercion from `ℤ` to `v.adicCompletion ℚ`.

